Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.50,0:01:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十六话 志志雄的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惊人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这艘炼狱战舰花费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全部财产的五分之三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒你们  我誓不罢休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙想用这艘船\N占据明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真佩服这些人能找到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个不认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些只会找碴的鼠辈\N跟我们比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是一群乌合之众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还敢到这里来搞乱\N真是自不量力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人  浑身打颤的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.53,0:02:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要怎样解决  那艘垃圾船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.47,0:02:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村  你能破坏那艘船吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.44,0:03:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在海里可能没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你破坏右船舷\N我来解决左船舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.65,0:03:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这打瞌睡就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.45,0:03:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  那么瞧不起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.72,0:03:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助\N我和斋藤去破坏敌人的大炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你趁机找小船接近战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.13,0:03:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用手榴弹破坏敌舰的后方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就和命运赌一赌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装上安式炮弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.38,0:03:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装上安式炮弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.06,0:03:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有时间去找小船\N等找到我都被炮打死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初击命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要装第二炮吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这次改装机关枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.72,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.00,0:04:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们是想成为\N不怕死特攻队吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会成全你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.04,0:04:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然被你们识破\N我的作战计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.31,0:04:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就将计就计  陪你们玩到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机关枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然用水柱抵挡机关枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪门子招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是雕虫小技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是新型手榴弹\N外壳看不起眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面却是威力强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.78,0:05:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克这家伙\N给我这么危险的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说能护身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过威力还真强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.29,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄  看我怎么收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.50,0:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点修复船身\N各单位报告损坏情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机关部损坏严重\N螺旋轴完全折断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船尾发生火灾  无法接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锅炉室浸水  无法阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火势逐渐接近弹药库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也要着火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治先生  请快下令退舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我千辛万苦\N才找来的这艘战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然败在这小子手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我曾考虑过\N他们破坏的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.77,0:06:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是绯村剑心的推理能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和斋藤的规划领导力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太低估他们两个的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是造成今天\N这局面的最大原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要占领日本\N非得除掉这三人不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新月村的决斗  如期计划吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,场地改成比睿山的鸟居寺庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们的老巢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.05,0:07:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和这十个江湖高手\N会等你们来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.99,0:07:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十比三的决斗  不太公平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.56,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二对二不是更快一决胜负吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正到船沉下去前\N有的是时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在比睿山的鸟居寺庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄先生  快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一次算我们扯平  但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.77,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会那么简单\N就放过你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们等着瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.01,0:08:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会要你们付出代价的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.25,0:08:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些船员不愧是\N志志雄的死忠部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.06,0:08:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有离他先逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.69,0:08:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在这里决战\N一定会有牺牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:09:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没必要造成别人的牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.14,0:09:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是太心软了\N这样怎么打败志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.88,0:09:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想\N造成无谓的牺牲罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.72,0:09:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我左之助在这  志志雄在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们别走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击沉炼狱战舰\N左之助是头号功臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.91,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实左之助比你\N想像中要可靠很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不用你说我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.58,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是那家伙本来\N就有点笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好火没烧起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都终于平安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.94,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百姓无人伤亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官死亡人数41名\N重伤者人数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.61,0:10:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,41人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.98,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比预计情况要好太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.55,0:10:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.19,0:10:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去料理善后\N你们去葵屋那里等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.43,0:10:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗改不了吃尿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.27,0:10:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使和他同为一阵线的人\N他还是一付臭屁样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.84,0:10:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实斋藤他也帮了我们不少忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不想和他和解吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:11:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你休想我和那家伙会和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等收拾完志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会和他决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.59,0:11:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快带我去葵屋\N被你气得肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在守卫  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 剑心回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.60,0:11:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心了  小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到小姐样子都变不一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是男孩子的风度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.45,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操和御庭帮的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气死了  气死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气死了  气死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天就这样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在我后面我居然会不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.74,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事就好了  昨天真的好危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说的人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身充满杀气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前绑着一块\N写着心眼带子的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盲剑宇水那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说那家伙冷酷无情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操居然能毫发无伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么  安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.14,0:13:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警备队已开始败阵\N我们没必要节外生枝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.01,0:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子正在爽的时候\N不必你来打扰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.75,0:13:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则连你也遭殃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.12,0:13:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了我们十个人的信条吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滥杀无辜不是我们\N需要做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们对阵了半刻钟左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.54,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后一言不发就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.14,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫安慈的\N和他们有点不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.25,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像志志雄那伙人\N那么冷酷无情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.19,0:13:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滥杀无辜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我就来和这家伙比比高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后的让我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.31,0:14:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是御庭帮的帮主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操  是剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好你也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快来人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是老翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁  爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.42,0:15:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让大家担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村  我有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道苍紫的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚阿操才说要告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我是拜托你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.55,0:15:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是有关苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.58,0:15:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫原本并不是现在这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我从小带大的所以我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是既聪明  又令人敬爱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在他一心一意\N想要成为江湖中最强的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思想已被私欲所蒙蔽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我无法阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果让他这样继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只怕会增添更多无辜牺牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了  绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四乃森苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就请你代我将他杀了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你已立下不杀人的重誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.02,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但除了将他杀掉之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.05,0:16:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别无其他方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已下定决心  对苍紫死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  你会杀死苍紫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.72,0:16:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解决魔鬼的唯一方法\N只有让他死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.49,0:16:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外别无办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫还没变成魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.47,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果苍紫已经失去人性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.78,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老翁现在不可能会起死回生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.62,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下意识的放松力道\N就表示他还有人性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.12,0:17:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍相信苍紫的天性是善良的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是解救苍紫  不是让他死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把他带回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的决定都没有考虑到阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是人老不中用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  斋藤派人传话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明早出发与志志雄决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村  苍紫的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样  明天早上爬得起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的睡眠  只要一刻钟就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刻钟  行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰有事找我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.81,0:18:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是有事想告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的决战终于要来临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流危不危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必为我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能不担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这关系到你的安危
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.94,0:19:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实飞天御剑流的精髓\N就是超神速的剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前几次由于我怕杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.61,0:19:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此力道减弱  剑速自然减慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.62,0:19:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就无法练成“天翔龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.46,0:19:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我已确知\N我本为剑客的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.82,0:19:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人的生死本就只有一线之隔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已不再惧怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自然也就练成“天翔龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只想完成\N打败志志雄心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.28,0:19:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是小惠保佑你平安的幸运物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只我和小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家都希望你平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  你要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打醒你这笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从刚才一直忍到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么好的气氛你不把握住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起码让剑心亲一下也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿小惠这烂东西出来\N煞风景干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.91,0:20:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说八道什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是阿燕那家伙\N叫你这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.98,0:20:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和阿燕无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦  你明天就在这里留守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又是我留守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.26,0:20:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.63,0:20:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果带你一起去\N遇到危险要开溜时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还得顾着你们万一出事谁负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.47,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你去在你离开东京以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.48,0:20:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勤练功夫\N现在身手已经一级棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.92,0:20:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要你留在这里留守啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们出发后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.66,0:21:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定志志雄\N会派人来突击这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.09,0:21:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要随时准备好\N才不会让他们乘虚而入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵屋的安全由我来负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.61,0:21:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你安心去吧\N还有苍紫就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.61,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是善变的人\N刚刚是谁还在大哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你罗嗦什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱哭鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就安心打败志志雄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.06,0:21:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一付信心十足的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有你们的支持与鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.91,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.59,0:22:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.04,0:22:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.77,0:22:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们等你回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定
